學校就讀的高中生。2014年在暑假結束後的開學第一天，他遭到來路不明的機器人襲擊，隨後被同學弓原雛保護並因不得已的原因強制被帶往未來（2088年）而遇到了一位名為隼鷹&middot;迪奧&middot;韋恩伯格的少年，他們的相遇改變這個世界的命運<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=NtOywCjt9gxtgongQE2YAF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=2e2fa950\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=NtOywCjt9gxtgongQE2YAF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=9816d3ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64aea4ad8f4b887307dae1e25d0dca3ca9d3b38b","tid":653604,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T01:29:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"321ac3f411f59a45fad12aab6ae0f2a2bd01726e","tid":653604,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T02:02:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"548df1a8d1d4c74fffff8e26aedd5e4bdbabad50","tid":653604,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T02:41:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16cdb8c5874c162fe7d60fa02701c9789b3b473a","tid":653604,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,